      "path": "audio/narrations/matrix-decomposition/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "这种分解揭示了矩阵的内在结构，也简化了许多计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "matrix-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
