      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/matrix-decomposition/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "今天我们将探索几种重要的矩阵分解方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "matrix-decomposition",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/matrix-decomposition/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "矩阵分解是将一个矩阵表示为几个特殊矩阵的乘积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "matrix-decomposition",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/matrix-decomposition/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.32,
      "size": 21168,
      "text": "不同的分解方法适用于不同的问题。"
